==== Add GitLab as system service

[source,bash]
----
sudo touch /etc/init.d/gitlab
----

Put the following content in that file

[source,bash]
----
#!bin/bash # chkconfig:
2345 95 20 # description: start gitlab # processname: gitlab

/opt/gitlab-6.2.3-0/ctlscript.sh start
----

Make it executable

[source,bash]
sudo chmod +x /etc/init.d/gitlab

Enable the service

[source,bash]
----
sudo chkconfig --level 2345 gitlab on sudo chkconfig \
 --add gitlab sudo chkconfig --list
----

Make sure you see a `gitlab` service with some `on`s in that line.

Reboot and check if gitlab is accessible from browser.
